RTX Libraries in this folder
----------------------------

* RTX_CM0.lib				- Standard RTX Library compiled with -O3 without debug symbols. Use this only when ASF_PROFILING is disabled in the project

* RTX_CM0_dbg.lib			- Standard RTX Library compiled with -O3 with debug symbols. Use this only when ASF_PROFILING is disabled in the project

* RTX_CM0_Prof.lib			- Standard RTX Library compiled with -O3 without debug symbols. Use this when ASF_PROFILING is defined in the project

* RTX_CM0_Prof_Dbg.lib		- Standard RTX Library compiled with -O3 with debug symbols. Use this when ASF_PROFILING is defined in the project
